  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9OaUtpVGFfMzIxNTYvc3RhdHVzLzE3MTE2NTg1MDAxODE2MzUxODA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/NiKiTa_32156/status/1711658500181635180\">https://twitter.com/NiKiTa_32156/status/1711658500181635180</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9kWTFQbHVPLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/dY1PluO.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dY1PluO.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dY1PluO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n10月7日2名在以色列工作的中国北京建工工人，在哈玛斯突袭中遭到攻击，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n武装份子要求他们下车趴下，其中王先生大喊我是中国人并没有起到作用，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n武装份子在他们表明身份后仍然开枪，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n王某身中2枪，后由以色列军警发现并以直升机后送至医院，目前状况稳定。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n与他一起遭到枪击的另一名工人则是下落不明。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br/>\n<br/>\r\n可能是沒有揮舞五星旗的關係<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9lT0tzWHRYLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/eOKsXtX.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eOKsXtX.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eOKsXtX.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9yYzR4SEh2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/rc4xHHv.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rc4xHHv.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rc4xHHv.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS93Sk0wZjJjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/wJM0f2c.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wJM0f2c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wJM0f2c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n犯我中華者 雖遠必豬<br/>\n<br/>\r\n喊我是中国人 多補兩槍\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
